{"componentChunkName":"component---src-template-post-tsx","path":"/intellij-검색/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"nodes":[{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-자동완성/"},"timeToRead":2,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 자동완성","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-리팩토링/"},"timeToRead":4,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 리팩토링","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-디버깅/"},"timeToRead":2,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 디버깅","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-Git-Github/"},"timeToRead":3,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] Git&Github","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-플러그인/"},"timeToRead":1,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 플러그인","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-소개/"},"timeToRead":3,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 소개","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-코드-Edit/"},"timeToRead":6,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 코드 Edit","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-포커스/"},"timeToRead":3,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 포커스","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-검색/"},"timeToRead":3,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 검색","series":"IntelliJ"}}]},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4a8877a5-91c7-5cb3-bb14-e9961c930323","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"banner\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7f3c4c668ea513e0950e70c83ed0a8d8/2bef9/banner.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7f3c4c668ea513e0950e70c83ed0a8d8/6f3f2/banner.png 256w,\n/static/7f3c4c668ea513e0950e70c83ed0a8d8/01e7c/banner.png 512w,\n/static/7f3c4c668ea513e0950e70c83ed0a8d8/2bef9/banner.png 1024w,\n/static/7f3c4c668ea513e0950e70c83ed0a8d8/c1b63/banner.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>해당 포스팅은 인프런의 <a href=\"https://inf.run/doaZn\">IntelliJ를 시작하시는 분들을 위한 IntelliJ 가이드</a> 강의를 참조하여 작성한 글입니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>검색 텍스트</h2>\n<h3>현재 파일에서 검색</h3>\n<p>현재 파일에서 우리가 원하는 검색을 하려면 일반 IDE처럼 맥 기준 <code>command + f</code>를 누르면 된다. 그러면 아래와 같이 나올 것이다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.453125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image01\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4e7dc0f0e23655bed8a6556c6d2a318c/2bef9/01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4e7dc0f0e23655bed8a6556c6d2a318c/6f3f2/01.png 256w,\n/static/4e7dc0f0e23655bed8a6556c6d2a318c/01e7c/01.png 512w,\n/static/4e7dc0f0e23655bed8a6556c6d2a318c/2bef9/01.png 1024w,\n/static/4e7dc0f0e23655bed8a6556c6d2a318c/71c1d/01.png 1536w,\n/static/4e7dc0f0e23655bed8a6556c6d2a318c/a878e/01.png 2048w,\n/static/4e7dc0f0e23655bed8a6556c6d2a318c/f7171/01.png 3456w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>현재 파일에서 교체</h3>\n<p>현채 파일에서 특정 검색어를 특정 단어로 변경하고 싶은 경우도 있을 것이다. 이런 경우 맥 기준 <code>command + r</code>을 눌러주면 아래와 같이 변경하고 싶은 검색어를 입력하고 하단에 변경하고 싶은 단어를 입력해주면 변경이 가능하다.</p>\n<p>여기서 replace버튼을 누르면 찾은 순서대로 변경이 되고 전체를 한번에 바꾸고 싶다면 replace all 버튼을 클릭하면 된다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.453125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image02\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/66a7ab8eb94cdee3abff299cbb7d184c/2bef9/02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/66a7ab8eb94cdee3abff299cbb7d184c/6f3f2/02.png 256w,\n/static/66a7ab8eb94cdee3abff299cbb7d184c/01e7c/02.png 512w,\n/static/66a7ab8eb94cdee3abff299cbb7d184c/2bef9/02.png 1024w,\n/static/66a7ab8eb94cdee3abff299cbb7d184c/71c1d/02.png 1536w,\n/static/66a7ab8eb94cdee3abff299cbb7d184c/a878e/02.png 2048w,\n/static/66a7ab8eb94cdee3abff299cbb7d184c/f7171/02.png 3456w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>전체에서 검색</h3>\n<p>전체 프로젝트에서 우리가 원하는 검색을 하려면 맥 기준 <code>command + shift + f</code>를 누르면 된다. 그러면 아래와 같이 특정 검색어를 전체 프로젝트에서 찾을 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.453125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image03\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/64a87560f0be190c7b8896c21ea57264/2bef9/03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/64a87560f0be190c7b8896c21ea57264/6f3f2/03.png 256w,\n/static/64a87560f0be190c7b8896c21ea57264/01e7c/03.png 512w,\n/static/64a87560f0be190c7b8896c21ea57264/2bef9/03.png 1024w,\n/static/64a87560f0be190c7b8896c21ea57264/71c1d/03.png 1536w,\n/static/64a87560f0be190c7b8896c21ea57264/a878e/03.png 2048w,\n/static/64a87560f0be190c7b8896c21ea57264/f7171/03.png 3456w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>전체에서 교체</h3>\n<p>전체 프로젝트에서 특정 검색어를 특정 단어로 변경하고 싶은 경우도 존재할 것이다. 이런 경우 맥 기준 <code>command + shift + r</code>을 누르면 된다. 그러면 현재 파일에서 교체처럼 변경하고자 하는 검색어를 입력하고 변경하고 싶은 검색어로 한 후에 검색을 해주면 된다.</p>\n<p>여기서 replace버튼을 누르면 찾은 순서대로 변경이 되고 전체를 한번에 바꾸고 싶다면 replace all 버튼을 클릭하면 된다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.453125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image04\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/403e71ff5be6592a1ea7f33ff7625a75/2bef9/04.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/403e71ff5be6592a1ea7f33ff7625a75/6f3f2/04.png 256w,\n/static/403e71ff5be6592a1ea7f33ff7625a75/01e7c/04.png 512w,\n/static/403e71ff5be6592a1ea7f33ff7625a75/2bef9/04.png 1024w,\n/static/403e71ff5be6592a1ea7f33ff7625a75/71c1d/04.png 1536w,\n/static/403e71ff5be6592a1ea7f33ff7625a75/a878e/04.png 2048w,\n/static/403e71ff5be6592a1ea7f33ff7625a75/f7171/04.png 3456w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>정규 표현식으로 검색, 교체</h3>\n<p>아래와 같은 코드가 있다고 해보자.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>ko<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>UTF-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Title<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>titleId<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>titleName<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>This is a Heading<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>application/javascript<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>/robert/main/app.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=